      "heading": null,
      "description": "Slice the courgettes into medium chunks at an angle. Cut the nectarine into segments. Lightly brush courgettes and nectarine with olive oil and grill them on a grill pan on a medium heat until golden brown and charred on both sides."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Meanwhile, whisk together all the dressing ingredients, saving a few mint leaves for garnish. Season to taste."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Divide the chickpeas in serving bowls along with the charred courgettes and nectarines, drizzle with the dressing and finish with more mint leaves. Season to taste with salt if needed."
    }
